{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_5","type":"agent_message","text":"I found the current frontend is still using component-local fetch effects plus a small app-shell store, so the main job is to replace ad hoc server loading with a deliberate server-state layer and add a separate live-session store on top. I’m reading the current session/home components, API client, and tests now so the new abstractions land where the app already expects them."}}
