{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_53","type":"agent_message","text":"The failing tests exposed two useful points: automatic query retries are masking the explicit error states this app already designed, and a router test was assuming the list payload had already landed when only the route shell had rendered. I’m tightening both so the new state layer matches the prior UX instead of changing it accidentally."}}
